{"tid":1884094,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★【武漢肺炎】德研究：病毒可殘留物體表面9天","createTime":"2020-02-17T11:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T11:45:22.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e97ac478b531c0ae03110ebeb015c732939cf44b","tid":1884094,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:33:30.000Z","msg":"<strong>2019冠狀病毒病（武漢肺炎、COVID-19）究竟要如何防疫，確認感染源及途徑尤其重要，德國一項最新研究指出，若以人類病原體能在無機物上附着並存活最多9天而言，新冠肺炎患者接觸過的物品及其表面，也有可能有相同現象。</strong><br />\n<br />\n該項研究由《醫院感染雜誌》（Journal of Hospital Infection）刊出，研究人員為進一步了解新型冠狀病毒，試圖從相似且研究較清楚的病毒進行分析，如沙士（SARS）和中東呼吸症候群冠狀病毒（MERS）。<br />\n<br />\n科學家針對SARS及MERS進行22項研究，發現在特定溫度範圍內，人類病原體在物體表面能夠存活的時間，最大值為9天（病毒量1000萬，塑膠表面，室溫），而作為對照，麻疹病毒在物體表面的存活時間通常為2個小時（病毒量5000，鋁表面，21度）。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，上述研究的病毒，通常在木頭、紙張、鋁、塑膠和玻璃上，能夠存活約4到5天時間，而這些物品或材質是人類每日生活中，極為常見且大量碰觸的東西。格里夫斯華爾德大學（Greifswald University Hospital）醫生坎普夫（G&uuml;nter Kampf）指出，通常這些病毒能維持較長時間的生命，得利於較低的溫度及較高的濕度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%AA%AA/435822/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%BE%B7%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E5%8F%AF%E6%AE%98%E7%95%99%E7%89%A9%E9%AB%94%E8%A1%A8%E9%9D%A29%E5%A4%A9-3%E7%A8%AE%E6%88%90%E5%88%86-%E6%AE%BA%E5%AE%83%E6%AD%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E8%25AA%25AA%2F435822%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6-%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592%25E5%258F%25AF%25E6%25AE%2598%25E7%2595%2599%25E7%2589%25A9%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E9%259D%25A29%25E5%25A4%25A9-3%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2588%2586-%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E5%25AE%2583%25E6%25AD%25BB&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbF3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=ae352ebe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%AA%AA/435822/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%BE%B7%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E5%8F%AF%E6%AE%98%E7%95%99%E7%89%A9%E9%AB%94%E8%A1%A8%E9%9D%A29%E5%A4%A9-3%E7%A8%AE%E6%88%90%E5%88%86-%E6%AE%BA%E5%AE%83%E6%AD%BB</a>"},{"pid":"4005dad797969c744d6db65b2d017f844d6fe6cd","tid":1884094,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:33:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2414c6bae46e15d312bae927424b606577c630b2","tid":1884094,"uid":293518,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:34:57.000Z","msg":"72小時仲唔夠而家變9日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ea7220f2b61e9b57f058664cac109df689109d","tid":1884094,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2414c6bae46e15d312bae927424b606577c630b2","tid":1884094,"uid":293518,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:34:57.000Z","msg":"72小時仲唔夠而家變9日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:40:18.000Z","msg":"遲d 90日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87810aa3529c37a265b91e35626a8d519eb50803","tid":1884094,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2414c6bae46e15d312bae927424b606577c630b2","tid":1884094,"uid":293518,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:34:57.000Z","msg":"72小時仲唔夠而家變9日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:40:43.000Z","msg":"之前改左嫁啦 5日<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma